## How to Verify
1.  **Check Logs**: View [scheduler.log](file:///Users/vidushipatel/Documents/Code/RAG%20Chatbot/phase_5_scheduler_pipeline/scheduler.log).
2.  **Trigger Update**: Manually change a value in [ingested_data.json](file:///Users/vidushipatel/Documents/Code/RAG%20Chatbot/ingested_data.json) and run `python3 scheduler.py`.
3.  **UI Sync**: Refresh [http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000) to see the "Last updated" timestamp change.

**The Groww RAG Assistant is now fully automated and verified.**
